 * 
</P>
<P>
 Hartford Whaler wing Kevin Smyth, who suffered a thumb injury in a fight in an 
exhibition game against the Buffalo Sabres, underwent surgery to repair 
ligament damage and will be sidelined six to eight weeks. 
