<P>
Column 
</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA092194-0081 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 081182 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
September 21, 1994, Wednesday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Calendar; Part F; Page 1; Column 2; Entertainment Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
