<HEADLINE>
<P>
CAMPAIGN CALENDAR 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 The Democratic Coalition will host a discussion on Proposition 187 tonight at 
the California Pantry restaurant, 120 E. Palmdale Blvd., Palmdale.Dinner and 
social hour begin at 6:15 p.m., with the program at 7:25 p.m. Information: 
(805) 945-2330. 
</P>
<P>
 * The National Women's Political Caucus, San Fernando Valley, will give its 
1994 annual Light Award luncheon at 11:30 a.m. Saturday at the Braemar Country 
Club, 4001 Reseda Blvd., Tarzana. Democratic gubernatorial candidate Kathleen 
Brown and Los Angeles City Councilwoman Laura Chick will be the special guests. 
Cost is $50 for members and $60 for non-members. Reservations: (818) 986-2225. 
