</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Di-Onte Smith 
</P>
<P>
 SCHOOL: Grant 
</P>
<P>
 SPORT: Football 
</P>
<P>
 YEAR: Senior 
</P>
<P>
 SEASON AT A GLANCE: The 5-foot-10, 180-pounder has rushed for a region-leading 
495 yards in 41 carries and scored five touchdowns in the first two games of 
the season. 
</P>
<P>
 WEEK AT A GLANCE: Smith gained 352 yards in 19 carries and scored three 
touchdowns to lead Grant (1-0-1) to a 20-15 victory over Marshall in a 
