<P>
 America West Announces New Fare Cuts: America West Airlines has launched 
another round of leisure travel fare reductions that could cut the price of 
some tickets by nearly half, but customers have to act fast.The airline is 
offering the reduced fares through Dec. 20, but travelers have only until 
Friday to buy tickets. The reductions require a 14-day advance purchase and a 
Friday night stay. The deepest discounts are available on Mondays through 
Thursdays. The discounts could cut the round-trip fare from Los Angeles to 
Chicago by 11% to $338, or from Las Vegas to Atlanta by 48% to $198. Rival 
airlines have usually matched the America West reductions in cities where they 
compete. 
