<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA092194-0214 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 081315 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
September 21, 1994, Wednesday, Orange County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Part A; Page 19; Column 4; Metro Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
