<DATE>
<P>
September 21, 1994, Wednesday, Orange County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Metro; Part B; Page 2; Column 6; Orange County Focus 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
