</P>
</LENGTH>
<HEADLINE>
<P>
COMMUNITY NEWS FOCUS: NEWPORT/COSTA MESA/IRVINE; NEWPORT BEACH; CITY TO 
CONSIDER HIRING LANDSCAPE CONTRACTOR 
</P>
