NEWPORT HARBOR STAYS ATOP VOLLEYBALL POLL 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Newport Harbor, winner of the Orange County Volleyball Championships Saturday, 
received all of the first-place votes to retain its No. 1 ranking in the State 
Coaches' girls' poll. The Sailors were the top team in the preseason poll. 
</P>
<P>
 The Sailors defeated Laguna Beach, ranked third in the state, 15-17, 17-15, 
15-4, in the finals Saturday at Edison High. Newport Harbor reached the 
championship match by sweeping Sunny Hills, Huntington Beach and Esperanza. 
</P>
