<TEXT>
<P>
 Popular Explorers: Mazda is negotiating with Ford Motor Co. for an allotment 
of four-door Explorers in the 1995 model year. Since 1990, Mazda has marketed a 
two-door Explorer as the Mazda Navajo, but Ford has steadfastly refused to ship 
it any of the more popular four-door models. 
</P>
