<P>
 Pacific Sunwear of California Inc.: The company said Tuesday it plans to open 
as many as 50 new stores in 1995.After the proposed expansion, the company will 
have about 173 stores in more than 25 states. Most of the new stores will be 
opened in Midwestern, mid-Atlantic and Southeastern states. The Anaheim-based 
