the planned expansion. Smith previously worked at Natural Wonders Inc. and the 
Gymboree Corp. Pacific Sunwear also hired Ron Ehlers as vice president of 
information services. Ehlers was previously employed at Woman's World Shops 
Inc., a women's specialty retail chain. 
